og.description: Question: I paid $8 for this unsigned print, purchased at a tag sale several years ago. The print, 7 inches high and 4 1/2 inches wide, measures 11 inches high and 9 inches wide in its gilded wood frame. Any information you can provide about the artist who painted the original as well as my piece's age and value is appreciated. - B.B., Atlantic City
